items.name: CREDIT_MASK
items.definition:
CREATE FUNCTION credit_mask(input varchar(19)) RETURNS output VARCHAR(19) LANGUAGE SQLSCRIPT 
AS
BEGIN
output = LEFT(:input,4) || '-XXXX-XXXX-' || RIGHT(:input,4);
END
